<h3>MS02 Big Data Analytics for Novel Materials Discovery <a href="Presentations" id="dialog-2239-link-50">(<u>Abstract</u>)</a></h3>
<div class="ui-accordion-content">

<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" class="preso">
<tr>
    <td style="white-space: nowrap">Organiser:</td>
    <td>Luca Ghiringhelli (Fritz-Haber-Institut der Max-Planck-Gesellschaft, Germany)</td>
</tr>
<tr>
    <td style="white-space: nowrap">Co-organiser:</td>
    <td>Matthias Scheffler (Fritz-Haber-Institut der Max-Planck-Gesellschaft, Germany)</td>
</tr>
<tr>
    <td style="white-space: nowrap">Field(s):</td>
    <td>Chemistry & Materials, Physics</td>
