<h3>MS09 Abstractions Interplay in Domain Frameworks to Tackle Heterogeneity <a href="Presentations" id="dialog-2239-link-54">(<u>Abstract</u>)</a></h3>
<div class="ui-accordion-content">

<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" class="preso">
<tr>
    <td style="white-space: nowrap">Organiser:</td>
    <td>Anshu Dubey (Lawrence Berkeley National Laboratory, USA)</td>
</tr>
<tr>
    <td style="white-space: nowrap">Co-organiser:</td>
    <td>Brian Van Straalen (Lawrence Berkeley National Laboratory, USA)</td>
</tr>
<tr>
    <td style="white-space: nowrap">Field(s):</td>
    <td>Computer Science & Mathematics</td>
</tr>
