<h3>MS10 Emerging Applications of Computation in Economics <a href="Presentations" id="dialog-2251-link-32">(<u>Abstract</u>)</a></h3>
<div class="ui-accordion-content">

<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" class="preso">
<tr>
    <td style="white-space: nowrap">Organiser:</td>
    <td>Simon Scheidegger (University of Zurich, Switzerland)</td>
</tr>
<tr>
    <td style="white-space: nowrap">Co-organiser:</td>
    <td>Kenneth L. Judd (Stanford University, USA)</td>
</tr>
<tr>
    <td style="white-space: nowrap">Field(s):</td>
    <td>Emerging Domains</td>
</tr>
