<h3>MS14 Radiative Transfer in Astrophysics; Methods and Applications to Multi-Scale Simulations <a href="Presentations" id="dialog-2253-link-59">(<u>Abstract</u>)</a></h3>
<div class="ui-accordion-content">

<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" class="preso">
<tr>
    <td style="white-space: nowrap">Organiser:</td>
    <td>Lucio Mayer (University of Zurich, Switzerland)</td>
</tr>
<tr>
    <td style="white-space: nowrap">Co-organiser:</td>
    <td>Romain Teyssier (University of Zurich, Switzerland)</td>
</tr>
<tr>
    <td style="white-space: nowrap">Field(s):</td>
    <td>Physics</td>
