<h3>MS15 Recent Advances on Scalable High-Order Finite Element Type Schemes for PDEs <a href="Presentations" id="dialog-2253-link-31">(<u>Abstract</u>)</a></h3>
<div class="ui-accordion-content">

<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" class="preso">
<tr>
    <td style="white-space: nowrap">Organiser:</td>
    <td>Stéphane Lanteri (INRIA, France)</td>
</tr>
<tr>
    <td style="white-space: nowrap">Co-organiser:</td>
    <td>Peter Bastian (Universität Heidelberg, Germany)</td>
