<h3>MS16 Software for Exascale Computing <a href="Presentations" id="dialog-2253-link-48">(<u>Abstract</u>)</a></h3>
<div class="ui-accordion-content">

<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" class="preso">
<tr>
    <td style="white-space: nowrap">Organiser:</td>
    <td>Harald Koestler (University of Erlangen-Nuremberg, Germany)</td>
</tr>
<tr>
    <td style="white-space: nowrap">Co-organiser:</td>
    <td>Matthias Bolten (University of Wuppertal, Germany)</td>
</tr>
<tr>
    <td style="white-space: nowrap">Field(s):</td>
