<tr>
    <td style="white-space: nowrap">13:30 - 14:00</td>
    <td><strong>Scientific Big Data Analytics at the John von Neumann-Institute for Computing (NIC)</strong>, Thomas Lippert (Forschungszentrum Jülich, Germany) <a href="" id="abstract-2253-dialog-link-512"><u>Abstract</u></a></td>
