		<!--  Text: [begin] -->
			<h2>Wednesday, June 3, 2015</h2>
<p>8:45 - 9:00    Audimax (HG F30) - Plenary Session
</p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><strong>Welcome to the Conference <em>Frontiers in Computational Physics</em></strong>, Remi Abgrall (University of Zurich, Switzerland)<strong><em><br /></em></strong></p>
<p>9:00 - 9:50    Audimax (HG F30) - Invited Plenary Presentation jointly organized with the conference <em>Frontiers in Computational Physics</em></p>
		<!--  Text: [end] -->
