<h3>MS03 Code Generation Techniques for HPC Earth Science Applications <a href="Presentations" id="dialog-2425-link-263">(<u>Abstract</u>)</a></h3>
<div class="ui-accordion-content">

<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" class="preso">
<tr>
    <td style="white-space: nowrap">Organiser:</td>
    <td>William Sawyer (Swiss National Supercomputing Centre (CSCS), Switzerland)</td>
</tr>
<tr>
    <td style="white-space: nowrap">Co-organiser:</td>
    <td></td>
</tr>
<tr>
    <td style="white-space: nowrap">Field(s):</td>
    <td>Climate & Weather, Solid Earth Dynamics</td>
</tr>
</table>

<br />
<strong>Presentations</strong><br />
