<h3>MS04 First-Principles Simulations on Modern and Novel Architectures <a href="Presentations" id="dialog-2425-link-267">(<u>Abstract</u>)</a></h3>
<div class="ui-accordion-content">

<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" class="preso">
