<h3>MS17 Applications and Algorithms for HPC in Solid Mechanics I: Plasticity <a href="Presentations" id="dialog-2439-link-258">(<u>Abstract</u>)</a></h3>
<div class="ui-accordion-content">

<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" class="preso">
<tr>
    <td style="white-space: nowrap">Organiser:</td>
    <td>William Curtin (EPFL, Switzerland)</td>
</tr>
<tr>
    <td style="white-space: nowrap">Co-organiser:</td>
    <td>Guillaume Anciaux (EPFL, Switzerland)</td>
</tr>
<tr>
    <td style="white-space: nowrap">Field(s):</td>
    <td>Engineering</td>
</tr>
