	</script><div class="title">Coarse-Grained Protein Model for Dissipative Particle Dynamics</div> <div class="table author-items submission-introduction"> <div class="tr"> <div class="td td-label">Presenter:</div> <div class="td"> <div class="authors inline"> <div class="author"> Igor V. Pivkin (Università della Svizzera italiana, Switzerland)</span> <script class="pasc-biography-item-json" type="text/template">
