	</script><div class="title">A Scalable Object Store for Meteorological and Climate Data</div> <div class="table author-items submission-introduction"> <div class="tr"> <div class="td td-label">Presenter:</div> <div class="td"> <div class="authors inline"> <div class="author"> Simon D. Smart (ECMWF, United Kingdom)</span> <script class="pasc-biography-item-json" type="text/template">
