	</script> <div class="title">Scalable Algorithms for Real-Space and Real-Time First-Principle Calculations</div> <div class="table author-items submission-introduction"> <div class="tr"> <div class="td td-label">Presenter:</div> <div class="td"> <div class="authors inline"> <div class="author"> Eric Polizzi (University of Massachusetts Amherst, United States of America)</span> <script class="pasc-biography-item-json" type="text/template">
